{"tid":999559,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"最重要是死前沒有後悔","createTime":"2019-01-28T19:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T20:12:11.000Z","uid":159946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a6d752b31ef07c534c73ebe9f7990915c943b2e4","tid":999559,"uid":159946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T19:58:49.000Z","msg":"當有感生命短暫時，才會更懂得珍惜今日。因為沒有人知道自己可以活多久，所以最重要是死前沒有後悔。而且他認為死亡這回事，對於正在面對死亡的人，和未面對死亡的人，其實分別不大：<br />\n<br />\n一個是被逼去想，一個是逃避去想。只是看你有沒有以正面態度面對死亡這件事。死前那刻，與現在的心路歷程理應一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2232190/見盡病人與死神搏鬥%E3%80%80莫樹錦醫生：最重要是死前沒有後悔?mtc=10027\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2232190%2F%E8%A6%8B%E7%9B%A1%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E8%88%87%E6%AD%BB%E7%A5%9E%E6%90%8F%E9%AC%A5%25E3%2580%2580%E8%8E%AB%E6%A8%B9%E9%8C%A6%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%EF%BC%9A%E6%9C%80%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%98%AF%E6%AD%BB%E5%89%8D%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E5%BE%8C%E6%82%94%3Fmtc%3D10027&d=RH6Ab9G4Smx3Ukb%2FUx9OADACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=d18a1c19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2232190/見盡病人與死神搏鬥%E3%80%80莫樹錦醫生：最重要是死前沒有後悔?mtc=10027</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkbodhigarden\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkbodhigarden&d=RH6Ab9G4Smx3Ukb%2FUx9OADACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=8f92c2c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkbodhigarden</a>"},{"pid":"a7ebf6ea7804405f961252f93d4a00fb254844a9","tid":999559,"uid":78429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T20:12:11.000Z","msg":"真係講易過做<br />\n後悔本身就係要去到某個位先會出現<br />\n而家就嚟死，死嗰刻仲要諗自己後唔後悔"}]}